{"tid":2273429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯:已致信特首促DQ【委任派】許智峯及林卓廷","createTime":"2020-11-05T17:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T14:40:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be6450a7698e6e900078d772f6857199faf96467","tid":2273429,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202011/05/AP5fa4161be4b0fbfd2536e541.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenweipo.com%2Fa%2F202011%2F05%2FAP5fa4161be4b0fbfd2536e541.html&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8sQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=92ec624e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202011/05/AP5fa4161be4b0fbfd2536e541.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/wwpproduct/image/202011/05/5fa415c5e4b07efb96ff526c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fwwpproduct%2Fimage%2F202011%2F05%2F5fa415c5e4b07efb96ff526c1.jpg&h=ea8f9edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大公文匯全媒體報道：立法會議員何君堯今日（5日）晚上10時30分在社交平台進行直播指，他已去信特首及律政司，促請撤銷攬炒派議員許智峯及林卓廷的議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/wwpproduct/image/202011/05/5fa415e0e4b07efb96ff52911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fwwpproduct%2Fimage%2F202011%2F05%2F5fa415e0e4b07efb96ff52911.jpg&h=26c8abe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，自立法會開始以來，攬炒派議員一直進行拉布，嚴重拖拉內務委員會以及18個事務委員會的主席選舉，更阻礙立法會大會的進程，瘋狂點算人數導致大會多次流會。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯指，特別在今天(5日)和昨天(4日)的立法會大會，攬炒派議員要求點算法定人數多達20次，當何君堯進行質詢時，許智峯及林卓廷更表現狂妄，企圖阻礙何君堯發言，嚴重拖慢議會進度，攬炒派議員特別是許智峯及林卓廷二人明顯違反了《基本法》第104條的宣誓內容，促請特首及律政司撤銷二人議員資格。"},{"pid":"94af3ea77e873f7440930b8c225ddaf10380476b","tid":2273429,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}